*Vredi* mu se truditi da postigne uspeh. (It is worth his effort to achieve success.)

*Vredilo* je čekati. (It was worth the wait.)

Njegova izjava *vredi* dosta. (His statement is worth a lot.)

Nije *vredilo* da čekam. (It wasn't worth waiting.)

*Vredi* da se pazite. (It is worth being careful.)

Treba da *vredi* napor. (The effort should be worth it.)